        <span>Print</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="policy" class="container" role="main">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Cyber Security Rtain LMS</p>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: <time datetime="2025-09-28">September 28, 2025</time></p>
    </section>

    <nav class="toc card" aria-labelledby="toc-heading">
      <h2 id="toc-heading">Contents</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#introduction">1. Introduction</a></li>
        <li><a href="#data-we-collect">2. What Data We Collect</a></li>
        <li><a href="#how-we-use">3. How We Use Your Data</a></li>
        <li><a href="#legal-basis">4. Legal Basis for Processing</a></li>
        <li><a href="#retention">5. Data Retention</a></li>
        <li><a href="#sharing-security">6. Data Sharing &amp; Security</a></li>
